<text id="02-output-contract" title="Product Analytics Output Contract" version="1.1.0" est_tokens="900" depth="essential">
  <summary>JSON Schema draft-07 for the spec artefact this methodology produces, with valid and invalid examples plus forbidden patterns.</summary>

  <section title="Schema (JSON Schema draft-07)">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-07/schema#",
  "$id": "https://faion.net/schemas/product-analytics.json",
  "type": "object",
  "required": [
    "plan_version",
    "events",
    "metric_tree",
    "anomaly_rules",
    "pii_policy"
  ],
  "properties": {
    "plan_version": {
      "type": "string",
      "pattern": "^[0-9]+\\\\.[0-9]+\\\\.[0-9]+$"
    },
    "events": {
      "type": "array",
      "minItems": 1,
      "items": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": [
          "name",
          "properties",
          "owner",
          "status"
        ],
        "properties": {
          "name": {
            "type": "string",
            "pattern": "^[a-z][a-z0-9_]+_[a-z][a-z0-9_]+$"
          },
          "properties": {
            "type": "object"
          },
          "owner": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "status": {
            "enum": [
              "live",
              "deprecated",
              "proposed"
            ]
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "metric_tree": {
      "type": "object",
      "required": [
        "north_star",
        "inputs"
      ],
      "properties": {
        "north_star": {
          "type": "string"
        },
        "inputs": {
          "type": "array",
          "minItems": 2,
          "maxItems": 3,
          "items": {
            "type": "object",
            "required": [
              "name",
              "causes"
            ]
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "anomaly_rules": {
      "type": "array",
      "minItems": 1,
      "items": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": [
          "metric",
          "threshold"
        ]
      }
    },
    "pii_policy": {
      "type": "object",
      "required": [
        "redact_at_ingest",
        "fields"
      ],
      "properties": {
        "redact_at_ingest": {
          "const": true
        },
        "fields": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {
            "type": "string"
          }
        }
      }
    }
  },
  "additionalProperties": true
}
]]></code>
  </section>

  <example valid="true">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "plan_version": "2.4.0",
  "events": [
    {
      "name": "checkout_started",
      "properties": {
        "plan_tier": "string"
      },
      "owner": "growth",
      "status": "live"
    },
    {
      "name": "checkout_completed",
      "properties": {
        "order_id": "string"
      },
      "owner": "growth",
      "status": "live"
    }
  ],
  "metric_tree": {
    "north_star": "weekly_active_paying_users",
    "inputs": [
      {
        "name": "activation_rate",
        "causes": "wapu"
      },
      {
        "name": "retention_d30",
        "causes": "wapu"
      }
    ]
  },
  "anomaly_rules": [
    {
      "metric": "activation_rate",
      "threshold": "wow_delta_abs > 0.03"
    }
  ],
  "pii_policy": {
    "redact_at_ingest": true,
    "fields": [
      "email",
      "phone",
      "ip"
    ]
  }
}
]]></code>
  </example>

  <example valid="false">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "plan_version": "v1",
  "events": [
    {
      "name": "ButtonClick",
      "properties": {}
    }
  ],
  "metric_tree": {
    "north_star": "DAU"
  },
  "anomaly_rules": [],
  "pii_policy": {
    "redact_at_ingest": false,
    "fields": []
  }
}
]]></code>
    <note>plan_version not semver; event name camelCase + missing object_action; missing event owner/status; metric_tree.inputs missing; anomaly_rules empty; PII redact_at_ingest false.</note>
  </example>

  <section title="Forbidden patterns">
    <list>
      <item>event name not matching `object_action` snake_case past-tense pattern.</item>
      <item>metric_tree.inputs fewer than 2 (no causal chain).</item>
      <item>anomaly_rules empty (soft-judgment anomalies).</item>
      <item>pii_policy.redact_at_ingest=false (late redaction).</item>
      <item>event without owner or status (orphan event).</item>
    </list>
  </section>

  <reference path="scripts/validate-product-analytics.py">Validator script enforcing this schema</reference>
</text>
